				<wikidot:authorName>wishun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1204404</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm heading to the leak thread right after this, thanks in advance for the mental relief.</p> <p>Edit:You realize that I hate you now, right?<br /> Edit<sup>2</sup>:No I don't. Famine is just too subtle, went right over my head.</p> <p>For me, American Beauty immediately popped to mind because it's a plastic bag blowing in the wind. Just a random, circumstantial conection with a scene from the movie. The tone here does vibe well with the surreal mundane-philosophy recollections I have of the movie, but I wouldn't have ever noticed that if the platic bag hadn't primed me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
